"- **┬¦88**: Automatically handles type coercions between different number types (ŌäĢ, Ōäż, ŌäÜ, ŌäØ), when the Goal is *exactly*\n"
"what you're trying to prove, just needs to get coerced.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## Pro Tips for This Level\n"
"\n"
"1. **Use ┬¦89** to convert ┬¦90 to its definition\n"
