"1. Use ┬¦13 to ensure ┬¦14\n"
"2. Use ┬¦15 so that ┬¦16\n"
"\n"
"**Key insight:** When proving continuity, factor the difference and bound each piece separately!\n"
"\n"
"This \"localize then control\" strategy is fundamental to ┬¦17-┬¦18 proofs. You'll see it again and again throughout analysis."
