"\n"
"So the subsequence is constant: ┬¦9 which clearly converges to 1!\n"
"\n"
"**New Tool: The ┬¦10 Tactic**\n"
"\n"
"To define ┬¦11 within our proof, we use the ┬¦12 tactic. This creates a new variable or function/sequence (unlike ┬¦13, which proves propositions).\n"
"\n"
"**The ┬¦14 Keyword:**\n"
"\n"
"To create a function in Lean, we use ┬¦15:\n"
"┬¦16\n"
