"1. Define ┬¦29 using ┬¦30\n"
"2. Use ┬¦31 and ┬¦32 as our witnesses\n"
"3. Prove two things:\n"
"   - ┬¦33 is a subsequence (strictly increasing)\n"
"   - ┬¦34 converges to 1\n"
