#: Game.Levels.L6Levels.L04_Cases'
msgid "# ­¤öä Case Analysis Mastered! ­¤öä\n"
"\n"
"Excellent! You've just learned one of the most powerful proof techniques in mathematics: case analysis. The ┬¦0 tactic embodies a fundamental principle of logical reasoningŌĆöwhen you don't know which of several possibilities is true, you prove your result holds in every case.\n"
"\n"
"**Why This Matters:**\n"
"Case analysis is everywhere in mathematics. From proving that every integer is either even or odd, to showing that continuous functions on closed intervals achieve their extrema, the ability to systematically consider all possibilities is crucial for rigorous reasoning.\n"
"\n"
"**The Beauty of Completeness:**\n"
"Notice how ┬¦1 forced you to handle both scenarios completely. This isn't just a formal requirementŌĆöit ensures that your proof is truly bulletproof. No matter which case actually occurs, your argument will hold.\n"
"\n"
"**Strategic Insight:**\n"
"In our example, both cases led to the same algebraic manipulation (┬¦2), but that won't always be true. Often, different cases require entirely different approaches. Learning to adapt your strategy to each case while keeping sight of the overall goal is a key mathematical skill.\n"
"\n"
"**Looking Forward:**\n"
"As we continue with convergence proofs and other analysis topics, you'll find ┬¦3 invaluable for handling statements like \"either the sequence is bounded above or below\" or \"either the limit exists or the sequence diverges.\" The systematic approach you've learned here will serve you well in these more complex scenarios.\n"
"\n"
"Mathematics is about leaving no stone unturned, no possibility unconsidered. With ┬¦4, you now have the tools to be completely thorough in your logical investigations."
msgstr ""

